		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform2" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=247125"><span id=Scholar>Jiggidyjay of the Seven Seas</span></a><b><span id=Scholar><br>Scholar</span></b><br /><img alt="Avatar" height="73" width="100" src="/uf/Jiggidyjay/Avatar2.jpg"><br /><br /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*"/><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><br />1475 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Good [3.52]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Jiggidyjay&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>If you got a skillup in singing, then the song you chose does not match your instrument. I would need to know which song you chose and which instrument you had equipped to know exactly what you did wrong. Each song has a specific instrument or singing skill associated with it, and if you don't choose the right instrument for the right skill, you won't be able to skill up in that skill.<br><br>When equipping instruments, if the instrument is a secondary only item, then you can not equip anything your primary slot. If it's is a primary/secondary item, then you can equip the instrument in primary and a weapon in the secondary, buf if you put the instrument in secondary, you can't put anything in your primary. Think of it like this: if you have an instrument in your secondary, it's like playing with two hands (even though you'll still punch with your primary hand if you turn on autoattack).</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br /><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1006062" target="akztarg">Jiggidyjay</a> - <span class="sm">Mr Ranger</span class="sm"><br><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1003866" target="akztarg">Zingin Ansinging</a> - <span class="sm">Mr Bard of <a href="HTTP://firestormers.com/viewnews.php" target="akztarg">The Firestormers</a></span class="sm"><br><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1006061" target="akztarg">Zolotaya</a> - <span class="sm">Ms Necro</span class="sm"><br><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1189723" target="akztarg">Zeibis</a> - <span class="sm">Mr Monk</span class="sm"></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from the Oval Office.</td></tr></table>
